{"type":"text","timestamp":1773446193951,"sessionID":"ses_316650d1dffespdzjLs3PfWdD3","part":{"id":"prt_ce9a1328d001rLu1Kqc1yXK1I4","sessionID":"ses_316650d1dffespdzjLs3PfWdD3","messageID":"msg_ce9a1298900122itRwHkOpa6AO","type":"text","text":"Good. Now I have a thorough understanding of the codebase. Let me now enhance the implementation files. The key areas to improve:\n\n1. **test-detection.ts** — Add better non-testable file exclusion for config files (.json, .yml, .yaml), documentation (.md), and other non-code files\n2. **prompt.ts** — Strengthen TDD red-green cycle enforcement with more specific instructions about commit flow and verification\n3. **tdd-verifier.ts** — Minor integration improvements\n\nLet me start with the enhancements:","time":{"start":1773446193951,"end":1773446193951}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1773446194511,"sessionID":"ses_316650d1dffespdzjLs3PfWdD3","part":{"id":"prt_ce9a1400a001zXrqYuqX9aq2M5","sessionID":"ses_316650d1dffespdzjLs3PfWdD3","messageID":"msg_ce9a1298900122itRwHkOpa6AO","type":"tool","callID":"toolu_vrtx_01CuHf7GG8MNnsqvfTuHzvh3","tool":"edit","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/tdd-red-green-coercion/src/lib/test-detection.ts","oldString":"/** Configuration for test detection */\nexport interface TestDetectionConfig {\n  /** Glob patterns for test file locations (relative to repo root) */\n  testFilePatterns: string[];\n  /** Source directory prefixes to scan (e.g., [\"src/\"]) */\n  sourceDirs: string[];\n  /** File extensions to consider as source files */\n  sourceExtensions: string[];\n  /** Additional filename patterns to exclude (beyond built-in exclusions) */\n  excludePatterns: string[];\n}","newString":"/** Configuration for test detection */\nexport interface TestDetectionConfig {\n  /** Glob patterns for test file locations (relative to repo root) */\n  testFilePatterns: string[];\n  /** Source directory prefixes to scan (e.g., [\"src/\"]) */\n  sourceDirs: string[];\n  /** File extensions to consider as source files */\n  sourceExtensions: string[];\n  /** Additional filename patterns to exclude (beyond built-in exclusions) */\n  excludePatterns: string[];\n  /** File extensions that are inherently non-testable (config, docs, data) */\n  nonTestableExtensions?: string[];\n}\n\n// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n// Non-Testable File Detection\n// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n/**\n * File extensions that are inherently non-testable.\n * These files contain configuration, documentation, data, or metadata\n * that do not produce runtime code and should not require tests.\n */\nexport const NON_TESTABLE_EXTENSIONS: readonly string[] = [\n  // Documentation\n  \".md\",\n  \".mdx\",\n  \".txt\",\n  \".rst\",\n  // Configuration\n  \".json\",\n  \".yml\",\n  \".yaml\",\n  \".toml\",\n  \".ini\",\n  \".env\",\n  \".env.example\",\n  \".env.local\",\n  // CSS / Styling (no logic)\n  \".css\",\n  // Assets / images\n  \".svg\",\n  \".png\",\n  \".jpg\",\n  \".jpeg\",\n  \".gif\",\n  \".ico\",\n  \".webp\",\n  // Build / project config\n  \".lock\",\n  \".editorconfig\",\n  \".gitignore\",\n  \".gitattributes\",\n  \".npmignore\",\n  \".prettierrc\",\n  \".prettierignore\",\n  \".eslintignore\",\n];"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","title":"src/lib/test-detection.ts","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/tdd-red-green-coercion/src/lib/verifier.ts":[],"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/tdd-red-green-coercion/src/lib/test-runner.ts":[],"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/tdd-red-green-coercion/src/lib/tdd-verifier.ts":[],"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/tdd-red-green-coercion/src/lib/test-detection.ts":[{"range":{"start":{"line":16,"character":37},"end":{"line":16,"character":45}},"message":"'relative' is declared but its value is never read.","severity":4,"code":6133,"source":"typescript"}],"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/tdd-red-green-coercion/src/lib/prompt.ts":[],"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/tdd-red-green-coercion/src/config.ts":[],"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/tdd-red-green-coercion/src/commands/verify.ts":[],"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/tdd-red-green-coercion/tests/features.test.ts":[{"range":{"start":{"line":57,"character":6},"end":{"line":57,"character":20}},"message":"Object literal may only specify known properties, and 'worktreePrefix' does not exist in type '{ branchPrefix: string; remote: string; mergeStrategy: string; }'.","severity":1,"code":2353,"source":"typescript","relatedInformation":[{"location":{"uri":"file:///home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-com